Chunk 4 complete. Created:

**`src/server/services/posting.ts`** — hybrid posting logic:
- `postContent(orgId, accountId, variationId, platform, postRecordId)` — main entry
- Routes by `accountType`: PRIMARY → `postViaApi()`, SECONDARY → `postViaBrowser()`
- API path: fetches OAuth token from Infisical (fetch-use-discard), dispatches to platform-specific stubs (YouTube, TikTok, Instagram, Facebook, X, LinkedIn)
- Browser path: loads fingerprint profile + proxy from Infisical, session from R2 (Patchright stubs)
- `finalizePost()` — updates PostRecord status, calls circuit breaker `recordSuccess`/`recordFailure`, emits SSE via Redis pub/sub `post:events`

**`src/server/workers/post-worker.ts`** — pg-boss consumer:
- Subscribes to `post:task` queue (teamSize=2, teamConcurrency=2)
- Validates PostRecord still SCHEDULED before executing
- `startPostWorker()` / `stopPostWorker()` lifecycle

